---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">About Us</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">This is just a simnple website used to display temperature and humidity data using an Arduino sketch with a network shield outputting data into JSON format. The Arduino sketch can be found here: <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/doodersrage/arduino-network-json-temperature-sever">https://github.com/doodersrage/arduino-network-json-temperature-sever</a></p>
    <p>Source for the front-end you're currently looking at can be found here: <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/doodersrage/garage-temp">https://github.com/doodersrage/garage-temp</a></p>
</Layout>
